data.description: Welcome to your charming 3 Bed, 1.5 Bath home in desirable Franklin Township.  Convenience, & comfort combine to create the perfect family home. This tri-level residence is in a highly sought-after neighborhood and is near excellent schools. With easy access to the interstate, you can get wherever you need to be in no time.  New roof, newer furnace and water heater.  The living room has a bay window which allows in plenty of light.  The lower level has ample space which gives you the flexibility to be used as you desire.
